{"tid":2286504,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[唔批記協遊行] 跟本全港要lockdown!","createTime":"2020-11-15T05:08:24.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-15T05:20:39.000Z","uid":33939,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"a69ea72df8c7f56f7305436e82265b5b1169a3eb","tid":2286504,"uid":33939,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-15T05:08:24.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"red\">記協副主席陳朗昇在聆訊時表示，今次事件「茲事體大」，記協願意付上資源和成本，以做到「最嚴格的防疫要求」，包括定明是次遊行只供新聞從業員參與，會要求參加者事先在網上實名登記，提供姓名、所屬機構及記協會員編號（如有），參加者亦需填上健康申報表及列明同行者。</span><br />\n<br />\n如果做到咁都話唔俾遊行，咁跟本返工都唔應該，仲有果啲乜撚嘢支持人大簽名班cap水怪。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/%e6%b8%af%e8%81%9e/article/20201113/s00001/1605251084043/%e8%a8%98%e5%8d%94%e7%94%b3%e9%81%8a%e8%a1%8c%e8%a2%ab%e6%8b%92%e6%8f%90%e4%b8%8a%e8%a8%b4-%e6%94%bf%e5%8b%99%e5%8f%b8%e9%95%b7%e6%8b%92%e6%89%b9%e9%99%90%e8%81%9a%e4%bb%a4%e8%b1%81%e5%85%8d-%e8%a8%98%e5%8d%94-%e6%a5%b5%e5%ba%a6%e5%a4%b1%e6%9c%9b\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25e6%25b8%25af%25e8%2581%259e%2Farticle%2F20201113%2Fs00001%2F1605251084043%2F%25e8%25a8%2598%25e5%258d%2594%25e7%2594%25b3%25e9%2581%258a%25e8%25a1%258c%25e8%25a2%25ab%25e6%258b%2592%25e6%258f%2590%25e4%25b8%258a%25e8%25a8%25b4-%25e6%2594%25bf%25e5%258b%2599%25e5%258f%25b8%25e9%2595%25b7%25e6%258b%2592%25e6%2589%25b9%25e9%2599%2590%25e8%2581%259a%25e4%25bb%25a4%25e8%25b1%2581%25e5%2585%258d-%25e8%25a8%2598%25e5%258d%2594-%25e6%25a5%25b5%25e5%25ba%25a6%25e5%25a4%25b1%25e6%259c%259b&d=eSah%2B3q63CE7QW%2BLxhD4%2BN%2BR0LtvndqJ8lr%2BzYsHiyM%3D&h=15c49250\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25e6%25b8%25af%25e8%2581%259e%2Farticle%2F20201113%2Fs00001%2F1605251084043%2F%25e8%25a8%2598%25e5%258d%2594%25e7%2594%25b3%25e9%2581%258a%25e8%25a1%258c%25e8%25a2%25ab%25e6%258b%2592%25e6%258f%2590%25e4%25b8%258a%25e8%25a8%25b4-%25e6%2594%25bf%25e5%258b%2599%25e5%258f%25b8%25e9%2595%25b7%2